<p>
    To promote contribution sprints, mentors volunteered at the mentoring booth
    in the exhibition hall during all three days of DrupalCon. Conference
    attendees who visited the booth learned about the Friday sprints. Mentors
    also recruited additional mentors, and encouraged everyone to get involved
    in contributing to Drupal.</p>

<p>
